description:
Did you just take a great photo on your iPhone? Frame all your precious moments and make your photos look the best before you share them with your friends. With Real-Time Photo Frames FREE, you can add style and class to your photos! 

FREE VERSION: Real-Time Photo Frames FREE is fully functional, but only has access to 20 frames. The remaining 80 frames are available in the Real-Time Photo Frames Pro version as well as the feature to upload photos from your camera roll. 

It’s really easy to use. Simply choose a frame, snap your photo and voila! Then share it by email, Flickr, Facebook or Twitter. What are you waiting for??


FEATURES:
- Share your creations with Social Media.
- Two finger pinch on photo to zoom, rotate or move to easily fit it in the frame. 
- High resolution frames.
- Attractive, easy to use interface.
-Photo automatically saves to in-app gallery.
-Optimized for iOS 6.0 

If you have anything to tell us, please contact us at info@milkdrinkingcow.com, we love to hear your feedback! Thank you and enjoy!
